 Estevez]] | Also executive producer |- | ''[[All the King's Men (2006 film)|All the King's Men]]'' | Judge Irwin | [[Steven Zaillian]] | |- | ''[[Slipstream (2007 film)|Slipstream]]'' | rowspan="3" |2007 | Felix Bonhoeffer | Himself | Also director and writer |- | ''[[Fracture (2007 film)|Fracture]]'' | Theodore "Ted" Crawford | [[Gregory Hoblit]] | |- | ''[[Beowulf (2007 film)|Beowulf]]'' | [[Hrothgar]] | [[Robert Zemeckis]] | |- | ''Where I Stand: The Hank Greenspun Story'' | rowspan="2" |2008 | Narrator | [[Scott Goldstein]] | Documentary |- | ''Immutable Dream of Snow Lion'' | | Riccardo Spinotti | Short film |- | ''[[The City of Your Final Destination]]'' | 2009 | Adam Gund | [[James Ivory (director)|James Ivory]] | |- | ''{{sortname|The|Wolfman|The Wolfman (2010 film)}}'' | rowspan="3" |2010 | [[John Talbot (fiction)|Sir John Talbot]] | [[Joe Johnston]] | |- | ''The Third Rule'' | Fabian Hogarth | Aundre Johnson | Short film |- | ''[[You Will Meet a Tall Dark Stranger]]'' | Alfie Shepridge | [[Woody Allen]] | |- | ''{{sortname|The|Rite|The Rite (2011 film)}}'' | rowspan="3" |2011 | Father Lucas | [[Mikael Håfström]] | |- | ''[[Thor (film)|Thor]]'' | [[Odin (Marvel Comics)|Odin]] | [[Kenneth Branagh]] | |- | ''[[360 (film)|360]]'' | John | [[Fernando Meirelles]] | |- | ''[[Hitchcock (film)|Hitchcock]]'' | 2012 | [[Alfred Hitchcock]] | [[Sacha Gervasi]] | |- | ''[[Red 2 (film)|Red 2]]'' | rowspan="2" |2013 | Edward Bailey | [[Dean Parisot]] | |- | ''[[Thor: The Dark World]]'' | Odin / Loki masquerading as Odin | [[Alan Taylor (director)|Alan Taylor]] | |- | ''[[Noah (2014 film)|Noah]]'' | 2014 | [[Methuselah]] | [[Darren Aronofsky]] | |- |''[[Kidnapping Freddy Heineken]]''<ref>{{cite web|last=Chitwood|first=Adam|title=Anthony Hopkins speelt Heineken in nieuwe film over ontvoering|url=http://www.ad.nl/ad/nl/1022/Celebs/article/detail/3440056/2013/05/13/Anthony-Hopkins-speelt-Heineken-in-nieuwe-film-over-ontvoering.dhtml|accessdate=May 13, 2013|date=May 13, 2013}