'''Arezki Hamza Dembri''' (born April 25, 1988 in [[Sétif]], [[Algeria]]) is an [[Algeria]]n [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a forward for [[US Biskra]] in the [[Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 2]].<ref>[http://www.dzfoot.com/joueur.php?joueur_id=1274&saison_id=13 La Fiche de Hamza DEMBRI - Football algérien<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120319003109/http://www.dzfoot.com/joueur.php?joueur_id=1274&saison_id=13 |date=March 19, 2012 }}</ref>

==Club career==
*2006–2008 [[ES Sétif]] {{flagicon|ALG}}
*2006–2009 [[CA Bordj Bou Arreridj]] {{flagicon|ALG}}
*2009–2010 [[USM El Harrach]] {{flagicon|ALG}}
*2010–pres. [[US Biskra]] {{flagicon|ALG}}

==Honours==
*Won the [[Algerian Championnat National|Algerian League]] with [[ES Sétif]] in 2007
*Won the [[Arab Champions League]] with [[ES Sétif]] in 2007 and 2008

